+# Codex Structure Migrator
+
+`codex_structure_migrator.py` is a safe migration utility for JSON configuration files.
+
+## What it does
+- Moves top-level `models` and `routing` into `engine.models` / `engine.routing`.
+- Renames provider keys:
+  - `apiKey` → `api_key`
+  - `baseUrl` → `base_url`
+- Normalizes string-based feature flags (`"enabled"`, `"off"`, etc.) into booleans.
+
+## Usage
+```bash
+python codex_structure_migrator.py path/to/config.json --dry-run
+python codex_structure_migrator.py path/to/config.json
+python codex_structure_migrator.py path/to/config.json -o migrated.json
+```
+
+## Notes
+- Unknown fields are preserved.
+- `--dry-run` prints the migrated JSON and a list of changes.
